data.description: MOTIVATED seller. Gorgeous Bonus Sun Room! Spacious home located in desirable Northchase community. HOA amenities include pool, playground area, tennis courts and patio pavilion site. Located on quiet side of Northchase away from busy College Road traffic. 2 car garage with additional driveway space for friends and family. Large fenced back yard, single side gate and a second DOUBLE GATE for moving large sized items. Storage shed, on concrete slab in back yard, perfect for additional storage. Bluebird irrigation system. After Florence newer roof, NO flooding. New AC July 2022, new double stove and microwave, Viking dishwasher. New flooring throughout home. Move right in.
